1297
01:32:17,032 --> 01:32:18,532
Il le tient.

1298
01:32:18,825 --> 01:32:20,242
Plaque-le !

1299
01:32:21,244 --> 01:32:24,079
Paumes à plat !
Pouces en l'air !

1300
