On est perdus, Tommy.

1391
01:40:04,957 --> 01:40:07,209
On n'y arrivera pas.

1392
01:40:09,212 --> 01:40:11,296
On reviendra pas en arrière.

1393
01:40:26,145 --> 01:40:27,813
Tommy...

1394
01:40:29,190 --> 01:40:31,274
